#

Stuffed Bell Peppers with Ground Turkey and Black Beans

$12.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten Free

Tags:

AmericanComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A colorful and hearty dish packed with protein, fiber, and flavor!

Ingredients

  • Bell Peppers: 4 large
  • Ground Turkey: 1 lb
  • Black Beans: 1 can (15 oz) rinsed and drained
  • Corn: 1 cup
  • Onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Chili Powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Shredded Cheese: 1 cup (optional)
